    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that still looks and feels fantastic? I'm parting with my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, runs like a dream, and has been super dependable for all my trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next big adventure. Come take a look\u2014you're going to love it!",
