      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that\u2019s served me so well. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for the right person to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 33800.0,
