    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a torque-sensing M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The valvetrain has been recently shimmed to factory specifications, and the suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows the light patina of a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
